{"tid":1507403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人知尋日5點幾6點幾嘅時候，荃灣公園入面發生咩事？","createTime":"2019-08-26T06:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T02:07:24.000Z","uid":30771,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1bbf91019a45d2fed5e0e8dbce65dfcaa85749dd","tid":1507403,"uid":30771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:40:38.000Z","msg":"「另外，我們認為，今日在荃灣公園集會期間，我們主辦方被警方無任何通知下，要求結束集會，及以驅散之名包圍並肆意使用武器襲擊參加和平集會的人士，此等如失控野獸般的行徑令人齒冷。<br />\n<br />\n即使警方就我們的遊行和集會發出不反對通知書，但最終仍用盡一切卑劣的手段打壓市民的反對聲音，做法極度無恥，視基本法27條賦予市民的集會及遊行權力如無物。」from 825 tg channel<br />\n<br />\n尋日發夢去咗荃灣公園嗰到參加集會，本身以為有不反對通知書實安全啦，點知去到5點幾6點嘅時候，成堆防暴企晒喺唔同嘅出入口，之後慢慢推進到集會嘅地方，趕人走。嗰陣，現場係一個記者都冇，發生咩事係冇人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底所謂嘅不反對通知書，仲有冇法律效力？"},{"pid":"ff4c8254ef793b574346f6c54ac3ef86be5f0045","tid":1507403,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:41:17.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY4eonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=f9ceb91c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"43411b57a037abb279290393177108958ef0dd10","tid":1507403,"uid":132611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:42:03.000Z","msg":"個個注意力都出哂去"},{"pid":"f9870dded8de94a073cb7862065df9149c0f6520","tid":1507403,"uid":30771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43411b57a037abb279290393177108958ef0dd10","tid":1507403,"uid":132611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:42:03.000Z","msg":"個個注意力都出哂去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:42:57.000Z","msg":"入面有好多和理非街坊 仲有小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1ff12b153e660695f240b078a420ed79b38510","tid":1507403,"uid":30771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:47:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d96b8b20062210f5d5dfba4ea553fb118b94c06","tid":1507403,"uid":30771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:50:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e05acf3081d69ca2121c20dbb0722d9fe7f7614f","tid":1507403,"uid":271056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:52:25.000Z","msg":"你地有無用手提電話錄返??"},{"pid":"ca268ca43d913c746f9515e169297f5d5de90c3b","tid":1507403,"uid":30771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e05acf3081d69ca2121c20dbb0722d9fe7f7614f","tid":1507403,"uid":271056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:52:25.000Z","msg":"你地有無用手提電話錄返??"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:02:40.000Z","msg":"見到有人有拍低"},{"pid":"aa10810c69f28885409986bc6430b79635ed5777","tid":1507403,"uid":30771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nGE4dZf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnGE4dZf.jpg&h=cb81c722&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPush"},{"pid":"bc08e88e66b923c49b972b6274c77382941a308b","tid":1507403,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:11:59.000Z","msg":"[突發]撐狗學生寫左封信比人民日報<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1506426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1506426</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n借推"},{"pid":"b8c83365192ffa723f38c753cc465af37c1762c0","tid":1507403,"uid":30771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:21:07.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"d776f00e605ccbff0c