9a42ab8d1","tid":1507403,"uid":78764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T09:08:14.000Z","msg":"1740狗係楊屋道放催淚彈，1750左右楊屋道有人大叫走呀，一大群人向如心廣場巴士總站方向跑，有大部分人往大窩口方向走，少部分人行出海旁集會地點，當時進入公園嘅路有3個方向企左防暴，大會開咪重複講：今日不反對通知書係去到8:00結束，我地係和平集會。<br />\n<br />\n當時已經淨返少量參加集會人士，有幾十個街坊係到鬧狗，有手足係海旁set左rb，班狗向前推，大家沿海旁條路出去"},{"pid":"e62e79e2f5db05b94634d70e2844f285d74f1d90","tid":1507403,"uid":78764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T09:39:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kLpLJHK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkLpLJHK.jpg&h=d151ca5d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdPovnL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdPovnL.png&h=cde0d52b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wSYMs9r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwSYMs9r.png&h=de561476&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"409dfac00b25214282e1032f56ca0f0128c9ed32","tid":1507403,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T09:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca8bd0356bd08dd8cb266add523de861b19f81d","tid":1507403,"uid":30771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:19:39.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0905c46e336810913195678a0b94838159526376","tid":1507403,"uid":30771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:05:08.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"38d606f348804a90527a72057d6133516f27c296","tid":1507403,"uid":293667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:05:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/4B5ZOzj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4B5ZOzj.gif&h=aa5f1c27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[所有人注意 行動幫推]星期一代表咩 係文宣日！工作又要開始了 繼續撕一貼十精神<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1507941\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1507941</a>"},{"pid":"7dcaa58ea80bf042a725f1e7dd15c09011d29c7c","tid":1507403,"uid":30771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:56:46.000Z","msg":"721 811"}]}